we have found too little information about pgcrypto with jsonb types, for instance: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/48916285/postgresql-encrypt-jsonb-data and the pgcrypto documentation don&#39;t say anything about jsonb types https://www.postgresql.org/docs/10/static/pgcrypto.html

